#: src/window.rs:371
msgid ""
"This release adds a context menu to row and column display modes and updates "
"the platform to GNOME 49."
msgstr ""
"An versyon ma addya unn rol kettesten dhe fordhow displetyans rew ha koloven "
"ha nowedhi an bynk dhe GNOME 49."

#: src/window.rs:372
msgid ""
"Added a context menu on the images, mirroring the tab context menu. This "
"makes the context menu accessible in row and column display modes where "
"there are no tabs."
msgstr ""
"Addys unn rol kettesten war'n avenyow, kepar ha'n rol kettesten tabb. Hemma "
"gul an rol kettesten hedhadow yn fordhow displetyans rew ha koloven ly may "
"yma tabbys vyth."

#: src/window.rs:373
msgid "Updated to the GNOME 49 platform."
msgstr "Nowedhys dhe'n bynk GNOME 49."

#: src/window.rs:374
msgid "Updated translations."
msgstr "Nowedhys treylyansow."

